text = "HOW TO PLAY

Use Arrow Keys to move Telvar through each level.

Collect all 12 Spell Pages to fill your Spell Meter.
When the meter is full, Banish Mode activates — ghosts flee and can be eaten for bonus points!

Collect Spheres of Darkness to instantly fill the Spell Meter.

Bonus Items:
- Aten's Grace: Reveals ghost positions for 5 seconds
- Coronium Shard: Double points for 10 seconds
- Sabatha's Heirloom: Hidden bonus in each level

Beware the Hound of Fenrir — it defeats you in one hit unless banished!

Complete all 6 levels to discover Telvar's fate."

